## ITrading

```python
class ITrading(ABC):

    @abstractmethod
    async def place_order(
        self,
        request
    ):
        pass

    @abstractmethod
    async def cancel_order(
        self,
        order_id
    ):
        pass

    @abstractmethod
    async def amend_order(
        self,
        request
    ):
        pass
```

